Error codes will be either:</br>
a) Wrong format of JSON</br>
b) Device serial number is required</br>
c) Group does not exist</br>

+ Request (application/json)

        { "sn": "12365",
          "groupCode": "004-001",
          "user": "Mark"
        }
        
+ Response 201 (application/json)

        { "id": "12362" 
        }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

        [
            { "errorCode": "E7" },
            { "errorCode": "E8" }
        ]
        
## Group's Device [/apis/multi/groupDevices]
### Create multiple links between group and given devices [POST]
Error codes will be either:</br>
a) Wrong format of JSON</br>
b) Device serial number is required</br>
c) Group does not exist</br>

+ Request (application/json)

        [{ "sn": "12365",
          "groupCode": "004-001",
          "user": "Mark"
        },
        { "sn": "32140",
          "groupCode": "004-001",
          "user": "Mark"
        }]
        
+ Response 201 (application/json)

        [{ "id": "19",
           "sn": "12365",
           "groupCode": "004-001",
           "user": "Mark"
        },
        { "id": "20",
           "sn": "32140",
           "groupCode": "004-001",
           "user": "Mark"
        }]

+ Response 400 (application/json)

        [{ "id": "19",
           "sn": "12365",
           "groupCode": "004-001",
           "user": "Mark"
